Home































Knightsbridge Asset Management, LLC is an independent, 100% employee owned, Registered Investment Advisor. The firm was established in 1998, solely managing individual portfolios for both private clients and institutions.  We are investment managers you can trust and talk directly with, not a faceless organization.
We invest opportunistically with a focus on capital preservation as well as rate of return. Contrarian in nature and informed by extensive internal research, we employ a value oriented investment discipline, seeking to capitalize on market inefficiencies and irrational investor behavior. Our investment track record dates back to 1992 and is independently verified.  And our personal and family wealth is invested alongside clients.




 
